Class RoomMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • geomason.RoomMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TileBasedMap

    public class RoomMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements TileBasedMap
    Author:
    Norman Langner This class constructs the static floor field in form of tiles and saves it into a file to prevent recalculation for every new simulation start.
